---
const siteName = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_NAME || 'yookahplus';
const description = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_DESCRIPTION || '';
const edition = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_EDITION || '';
const tagline = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_TAGLINE || '';
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
const lang = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_LANG || 'en';

const aiDisclosure = lang === 'ko'
  ? '본 사이트의 콘텐츠는 AI 도구의 보조를 받아 작성됩니다. 모든 데이터는 1차 자료에서 검증되며, 본문 인용 링크로 직접 확인할 수 있습니다.'
  : 'Content on this site is produced with AI assistance. All data points are verified against primary sources, and all sources are linked inline for direct verification.';

const affiliateDisclosure = lang === 'ko'
  ? '쿠팡파트너스 활동의 일환으로 일정액의 수수료를 제공받습니다.'
  : 'As an Amazon Associate and other affiliate partner, we earn from qualifying purchases.';
---

<footer class="border-t border-border mt-24 md:mt-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- 미세 grain texture -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]" aria-hidden="true"
       style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(var(--color-foreground)) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 64px 100%;"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-20 md:pt-28 pb-12 relative">
    {/* 荑좏뙜 ?뚰듃?덉뒪 carousel (Korean lang only) */}
    {lang === 'ko' && (
      <section class="mb-16 md:mb-20 pb-12 border-b border-border" aria-label="荑좏뙜?뚰듃?덉뒪 異붿쿇 ?곹뭹">
        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-4">
          쨋 荑좏뙜 ?뚰듃?덉뒪 異붿쿇 ??異쒖궛쨌?≪븘 踰좎뒪??        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center overflow-x-auto">
          <script is:inline async src="https://ads-partners.coupang.com/g.js"></script>
          <script is:inline>
            new PartnersCoupang.G({"id":987938,"template":"carousel","trackingCode":"AF9652344","width":"680","height":"140","tsource":""});
          </script>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-muted-foreground mt-4 text-center">
          ???ъ뒪?낆? 荑좏뙜?뚰듃?덉뒪 ?쒕룞???쇳솚?쇰줈, ?쇱젙?≪쓽 ?섏닔猷뚮? ?쒓났諛쏆뒿?덈떎.
        </p>
      </section>
    )}

    <!-- masthead — 거대 wordmark -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-x-6 md:gap-x-8 mb-16 md:mb-20 items-end">
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8">
        {edition && (
          <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-4">
            {edition} · Colophon
          </p>
        )}
        <h2
          class="text-[18vw] md:text-[12vw] lg:text-[10vw] font-bold leading-[0.85] tracking-[-0.03em] mb-4"
          style="font-family: var(--font-display);"
        >
          {siteName}
        </h2>
        {tagline && (
          <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-md">
            {tagline}
          </p>
        )}
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4 md:text-right mt-8 md:mt-0">
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-2">
          MMXXVI
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs md:ml-auto">
          {description}
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- nav 그리드 — 더 미니멀 -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-12 pt-12 md:pt-16 border-t border-border">
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-5">Sections</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">About</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-5">Editorial</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/editorial-process" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Editorial Process</a></li>
          <li><a href="/editorial-standards" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Editorial Standards</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-5">Legal</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/affiliate-disclosure" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Affiliate</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Privacy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:underline underline-offset-4 decoration-from-font">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono mb-5">Follow</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href={import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_PINTEREST || '#'} class="hover:underline underline-offset-4">Pinterest →</a></li>
          <li><a href={import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_INSTAGRAM || '#'} class="hover:underline underline-offset-4">Instagram →</a></li>
          <li><a href={import.meta.env.PUBLIC_SITE_YOUTUBE || '#'} class="hover:underline underline-offset-4">YouTube →</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- AI disclosure — editorial styled -->
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-4">
          <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono">
            ¶ Disclosure
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-span-12 md:col-span-8 space-y-3 text-sm text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
          <p>{aiDisclosure}</p>
          <p>{affiliateDisclosure}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- bottom rail -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-3 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-muted-foreground font-mono">
      <span>© {currentYear} {siteName} · All rights reserved</span>
      <span>Set in {' '}
        <span style="font-family: var(--font-display);" class="normal-case tracking-tight text-sm">
          {/* fontDisplay 이름은 CSS variable이라 표시 어려우니 일반 표기 */}
          serif &amp; sans
        </span>
        {' '} · Built with Astro
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
